    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add most of your<strong> crab meat </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic paste </strong>and<strong> half</strong> your <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> with the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s]</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 30 secs further</p><p>Reduce the heat to low – this is your <strong>crab sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1572.-step-4-x200.jpg",
