      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>soaked noodles</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy noodle water</strong>, then add the <strong>drained noodles </strong>to the crab sauce with the <strong>wilted spring greens</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until fully combined – these are your <strong>chilli crab & spring green noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of the starchy noodle water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1572.-step-6-x200.jpg",
